(Lesson Vocabulary) Tj
T*
(- Essay Writing: The main topic being studied, understood here as develop effective) Tj
T*
(writing techniques.) Tj
T*
(- Core Focus: The main idea the learner must understand in this lesson: planning,) Tj
T*
(coherence, paragraph development, and support.) Tj
T*
(- Application: The point where the explanation is used in practice, such as building a) Tj
T*
(paragraph with a topic sentence and supporting points.) Tj
T*
(- Common Error: A repeated learner difficulty in this topic, for example listing ideas) Tj
T*
(without linking them logically.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Common Mistakes) Tj
T*
(- Misunderstanding the core focus of Essay Writing: planning, coherence, paragraph) Tj
T*
(development, and support.) Tj
T*
(- Listing ideas without linking them logically.) Tj
T*
(- Jumping to an answer without showing the steps or reasoning clearly.) Tj
T*
(- Practising Essay Writing without checking whether the method matches the question) Tj
T*
(being asked.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Quick Check) Tj
T*
(- In your own words, what does Essay Writing mean in English?) Tj
T*
(- What part of this lesson explains planning, coherence, paragraph development, and) Tj
T*
(support most clearly?) Tj
T*
(- Why is building a paragraph with a topic sentence and supporting points a good example) Tj
T*
(for studying Essay Writing?) Tj
T*
(- How would you avoid the mistake described as listing ideas without linking them) Tj
T*
(logically?) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Study Tips After Reading) Tj
T*
(- Rewrite the overview of Essay Writing in your own words after studying it.) Tj
T*
(- Use short exercises built around paragraph and full-essay structure before trying) Tj
T*
(harder tasks.) Tj
T*
(- Keep track of mistakes such as listing ideas without linking them logically and write) Tj
T*
(the correction beside each one.) Tj
T*
(- Revise Essay Writing regularly so the method behind planning, coherence, paragraph) Tj
T*
(development, and support becomes familiar.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Independent Practice) Tj
T*
(- Explain the overview of Essay Writing and describe how it fits into English.) Tj
T*
(- Work through an example based on building a paragraph with a topic sentence and) Tj
T*
(supporting points and explain each step.) Tj
T*
(- Describe why listing ideas without linking them logically causes errors and how to) Tj
T*
(avoid it.) Tj
T*
