T*
(Essay Writing is a valuable part of English. Students perform better when they) Tj
T*
(understand planning, coherence, paragraph development, and support, learn from examples) Tj
T*
(such as building a paragraph with a topic sentence and supporting points, and) Tj
T*
(deliberately avoid mistakes like listing ideas without linking them logically. Regular) Tj
T*
(practice built around paragraph and full-essay structure makes the topic easier to) Tj
